    <item>
      <title>加纳有望因推迟的欧洲债券改革而赢得国际货币基金组织的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/ghana-on-track-to-win-imf-blessing-for-delayed-eurobond-revamp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于加纳经济增长强于预期，上个月被国际货币基金组织拒绝的加纳 130 亿美元欧洲债券债务重组计划已重回正轨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/ghana-on-track-to-win-imf-blessing-for-delayed-eurobond-revamp</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:23:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非洲金融公司可能出售兰特及其他本币债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/africa-finance-corp-may-sell-rand-other-local-currency-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲金融公司是一家专注于基础设施的发展金融机构，正在考虑以非洲大陆货币发行债券，并正在商谈以南非兰特出售证券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/africa-finance-corp-may-sell-rand-other-local-currency-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:14:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦预计今年经济增长将低于目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/pakistan-expects-economy-will-grow-slower-than-target-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦预计今年截至6月的经济将增长2.38%，低于预算中宣布的3.5%的目标。]]></description>
